Provides media handlers for the MPO file format.

Class Summary
MPOFiles Utility methods for MPOFiles.

Package org.monte.media.mpo Description

Provides media handlers for the MPO file format.

Multi-picture File Format (MPO) as generated by the Fujfilm Real 3D W1 camera.
